caption:
April, 2023.

I only realised how long this month was once I started selecting photos for this post. 

I was ready to write about how this month wasn't that good (exams), but now I can't believe how I'd ever say that. It was a bloody rollercoaster with two exam weeks and events filled in everywhere.

This next week will be my last week of lectures for the first year. There's so much that has happened and yet so much left to do.

(Mujhe firse ghar jaana hai.)
